Package: gnucashr
Title: Read, Analyze, and Model GnuCash Accounting Data in R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jess", "Sullivan", , "jess@sulliwood.org", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Read GnuCash SQLite and XML files directly into R for financial
    analysis. Provides R6 classes for accounts, transactions, and books with
    multi-book consolidation, intercompany elimination, and monadic error
    handling. Includes Rcpp-accelerated fraction arithmetic and tree traversal.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Language: en-US
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
